{"tid":153391,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"我有個日式拉麵既疑問","createTime":"2017-03-12T14:12:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-30T04:49:53.000Z","uid":90166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"78878e7ebbd428072e107139ac0a41379dc7141c","tid":153391,"uid":90166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T14:12:43.000Z","msg":"話說我細個食日式拉麵（例如別府拉麵），d麵麵係黃黃地色<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/12/221117_c259138efbc3395b63c620c96603833a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F12%2F221117_c259138efbc3395b63c620c96603833a.jpg&h=59be5487&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n如上圖<br />\n<br />\n其實呢隻係日本邊個地區ge拉麵？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為我睇而家食親都係白色既麵，例如一蘭。"},{"pid":"6da0c4dfded57fd403a36ece6a0edef68d936a87","tid":153391,"uid":7033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T15:09:08.000Z","msg":"同問lm"},{"pid":"d58910fa145a3f77d7232b13622b361bcd9a7a8b","tid":153391,"uid":1275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T17:21:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>話說我細個食日式拉麵（例如別府拉麵），d麵麵係黃黃地色<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/12/221117_c259138efbc3395b63c620c96603833a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F12%2F221117_c259138efbc3395b63c620c96603833a.jpg&h=59be5487&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n如上圖<br />\n<br />\n其實呢隻係日本邊個地區ge拉麵？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為我睇而家食親都係白色既麵，例如一蘭。</blockquote><br />\n呢隻應該係醬油/味嶒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6ca57d7be8851acc225d51d41d286b839fc3e0e","tid":153391,"uid":8203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T17:24:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/13/012425_b5366ac87b8381803c121317328d755b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F13%2F012425_b5366ac87b8381803c121317328d755b.jpg&h=e7113050&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢碗係高山拉麵"},{"pid":"14eecc0be765cc2696cd32c7213e1419a896f1fd","tid":153391,"uid":60858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T21:13:58.000Z","msg":"博多拉麵好似都係幼麵，即係白色直身嗰種。北海道就好似都係粗麵，黃身曲嘅"},{"pid":"cff772fbdcb1318bce83f82b5a75e239d80d3f18","tid":153391,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T21:18:01.000Z","msg":"有加蛋同冇加蛋嘅分別<br />\n<br />\n利申:幾年前睇哂一套拉麵王"},{"pid":"8b16589244c5f808eb29e9eb9edf22b317defa16","tid":153391,"uid":73404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T21:20:03.000Z","msg":"如果你想講<br />\n黃色 曲 比較粗 重小麥味<br />\n應該係札幌拉麵(北海道)<br />\n白色幼麵係博多拉麵(九洲)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係唔知點解近年香港興呢隻 我不嬲鍾意食札幌多d"},{"pid":"490d10b453d548fac5774c542862f7193ae4e072","tid":153391,"uid":42178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T01:01:49.000Z","msg":"有分好多種麵<br />\n細至粗，曲同直<br />\n一蘭果種係直幼<br />\n黃色既有幼有粗，但普遍都係曲"},{"pid":"f876205bcf4fc141b55e4174f3d7b2e27d3cf6bf","tid":153391,"uid":90166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T01:28:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果你想講<br />\n黃色 曲 比較粗 重小麥味<br />\n應該係札幌拉麵(北海道)<br />\n白色幼麵係博多拉麵(九洲)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係唔知點解近年香港興呢隻 我不嬲鍾意食札幌多d</blockquote><br />\n我都係鐘意黃色 曲 比較粗 既拉面多d<br />\n不過而家反而少見!"},{"pid":"4caa0b69c10a8b9f133e9569bec07a1d206f56da","tid":153391,"uid":33336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T04:49:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}